  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK698">
<l>iḷaiya riṉamuṟaiya reṉṟikaḻār niṉṟa</l>
<l>voḷiyō ṭoḻukap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ministers should behave in accordance with the (Divine) light in the person of kings and not despise them saying, "He is our junior (in age) and connected with our family!".</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
